{"tid":1252653,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇喺澳洲嘅朋友想養狗","createTime":"2019-06-23T06:26:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T11:33:19.000Z","uid":161734,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a3ab670c65c6fbc586fef6292d779b2dbf756ba6","tid":1252653,"uid":161734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:26:22.000Z","msg":"係一隻流浪嘅貴婦狗 初頭以為係走失 帶返屋企先算 <br />\n後尾發現係主人唔要 幫佢執到靚靚之後掉街邊 但屋企已經有一狗 所以冇能力再養 依家暫時放寵物洒店 幫佢搵緊新主人 亦希望喺呢到博個機會 睇下有冇好心人<br />\n<br />\n5歲貴婦狗 身上有啲傷痕 眼睛有白膜 但好乖好聽話<br />\n<br />\n如果到最後都搵唔到主人 又養唔起 想請教下重有咩方法 唔想掉番路邊"},{"pid":"7c6cda6578cc98924f67b688a7b429bdb068daf8","tid":1252653,"uid":161734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:28:13.000Z","msg":"推一推 真係唔知點算好"},{"pid":"da8874b8c87d8e1e37d24799a4f52546f506b92e","tid":1252653,"uid":161734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:28:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c820b9fee333f37ba93aa1b75b66a96def4c6fca","tid":1252653,"uid":161734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:28:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2fe56046e5fe7685091a8fd6b1d93461f42e1f6","tid":1252653,"uid":161734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:28:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1368baebff0be86fc9f90d9b1de4b1ee6e1c221","tid":1252653,"uid":161734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:29:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f0b07718102c08664b4db7b4c80d8b61965566b","tid":1252653,"uid":161734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:29:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"987098c07cc75b46f2d76ca5c0653b20be8b9200","tid":1252653,"uid":161734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:30:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df950bdee7e4afbf8a95a61f34d102be6f9591d8","tid":1252653,"uid":161734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:30:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3488a92d322943b94223e0eaa433275a4e258c8d","tid":1252653